SPELL NAME  : Spiritual Hammer
SPELL SYNTAX: Hammer
SPELL COST  : 10+5*GL SP
DESCRIPTION : This spell calls forth the powers of good and embodies
              them in the form of a great hammer. The hammer is not 
              permanent, but instead, lasts for a duration based upon the
              Cleric's guild level. You may 'unsummon' your hammer, should
              you be so inclined.
